{"tid":2383781,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"3分鐘MV連換11套！IU破尺度「低胸超狂禮服」美到炸","createTime":"2021-01-28T06:32:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T09:03:44.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cb6c535ad81493f912f28a3461fd831b34ac4ce0","tid":2383781,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:32:34.000Z","msg":"南韓「國民妹妹」IU李知恩，能唱、能演、又會創作，圈粉無數、人氣超高！今（27日）終於回歸歌壇，推出新單曲《Celebrity》，這是她睽違四年的第五張正規專輯，MV中連換11套造型，身穿多套華麗服裝彷彿《德魯納酒店》中的滿月社長再現，驚豔眾人目光。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/27/3003688-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F27%2F3003688-PH.jpg&h=20b89c77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲IU李知恩回歸歌壇。（圖／截圖自1theK (원더케이) YT）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/27/3003690-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F27%2F3003690-PH.jpg&h=01de315d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIU清甜嗓音獻唱《Celebrity》，依舊有著她甜甜的風格，節奏曲風輕快，讓人一聽就覺得好甜好溫暖，而在服裝方面IU超級用心，在短短三分多鐘的MV裡，IU一連換了11種不同風格的華麗造型，有復古公主風、蕾絲長洋裝、流蘇亮片洋裝和酷酷的西裝外套造型等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/27/3003686-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F27%2F3003686-PH.jpg&h=72ceb771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/27/3003692-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F27%2F3003692-PH.jpg&h=59b2889c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/27/3003694-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F27%2F3003694-PH.jpg&h=b10742df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IU李知恩共換了11套造型，還有破尺度低胸裝。（圖／截圖自1theK (원더케이) YT）<br />\n<br />\n尤其最後一幕，她身穿大紅落地長禮服，搭配華麗皇冠，黑色皮質手套在路上奔跑，頭髮盤起的高貴模樣，更是美出新高度，狂露天鵝頸和直角肩實在太美，讓粉絲直呼「女神好美！」、「可鹽可甜！是滿月社長沒錯」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/27/3003685-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F27%2F3003685-PH.jpg&h=eb2cd170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IU李知恩低胸紅禮服現身。（圖／截圖自1theK (원더케이) YT）<br />\n<br />\n不只服裝，她在妝容上面也很用心，在雙眼皮上點了一顆「小黑痣」，對鏡頭盡情拋媚眼，看來這款「IU黑痣妝」又將造成女孩們的模仿潮了！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/27/3003689-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F27%2F3003689-PH.jpg&h=e13643b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IU李知恩「小黑痣」妝容。（圖／截圖自1theK (원더케이) YT）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/27/3003697-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F27%2F3003697-PH.jpg&h=28e524de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0-q1KafFCLU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0-q1KafFCLU&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cU0YnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=2529424b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0-q1KafFCLU</a>"},{"pid":"70080d03ab7b53d92872429eae21a10dd2d6501b","tid":2383781,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:33:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e07e57cdf0327d6f43de7081c1e2dbcbe0cfea3","tid":2383781,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:33:14.000Z","msg":"勁正...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90770f23d37270465aa05be89729fb7899396347","tid":2383781,"uid":234509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:33:19.000Z","msg":"勁有氣質<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757211255d0362f951f03fc39e4c0f31e1191250","tid":